original_title: "It Is Not My Music": Don Cherry Swedish TV Documentary 1978
overview: Swedish TV documentary from 1978 Produced and directed by Urban Lasson  This film from 1978 is about Don and Moki Cherry and others who lived with them in the school house in Tågarp, Skåne, Sweden, in the 1970s and onwards. It includes sequences from SoHo, New York, and Moki Cherry’s textiles on the walls in Hästveda and Long Island City.
title: "It Is Not My Music": Don Cherry Swedish TV Documentary 1978
